Michael Bacall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Bacall 0 Michael Bacall (born Michael Stephen Buccellato; April 19, 1973) is an American screenwriter and actor, known for having co-written the films Scott Pilgrim vs. the World, 21 Jump Street, and Project X.
